OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCawston Park: Vulnerable   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpatient deaths prompt      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhospitals warning          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The deaths of three adults with        
OL,6, learning disabilities at a failed      
OL,7, hospital should prompt a review to     
OL,8, prevent further "lethal outcomes" at   
OL,9, similar facilities, a report said.     
OL,11,FThere were significant failures in the 
OL,12,Fcare of the patients at Jeesal Cawston 
OL,13,FPark, Norfolk, it found.               
OL,15,FNorfolk Safeguarding Adults Board      
OL,16,Fconcluded such hospitals should "cease 
OL,17,Fto receive public money".              
OL,19,FThe owner of Cawston Park said it was  
OL,20,F"deeply sorry" to the families.        
